name: Tucker Andrew
description:
This has been an interesting journey and i’ve learned more about myself than i thought was possible
i have met some women but haven’t met one person i will like to spend the rest of my life with…
though i’m new to this, but i hope it is a wonderful venue to meet people you won’t ordinarily meet its hard to describe yourself on paper, in one simple phone call or date. i offer loyalty, honesty, and respect, and a great sense of humor. when i feel strongly or i am happy, i tend to be passionate and intense, i’m very open and direct about everything. i’m young for my age, short black hair, wonderful eyes, emotional, i am quick witted and slightly sarcastic but i have an extremely soft and caring heart, and also romantic.i am weak and i am strong, i cry however, i laugh a lot more, i make other people laugh even a lot more..
